ğŸŒŸ Light Control
Mode	Behavior
OFF	Always off
AUTO	Turns on with motion; auto-off after timeout
FORCE ON	Always on, regardless of motion

ğŸŒ€ Fan Control
Mode	Behavior
OFF	Always off
AUTO	Speed auto-adjusts via Heat Index
MANUAL	User selects level: 0%, 25%, 50%, 75%, 100%

